         <div type="translation" xml:space="preserve"><head>Translation</head>
            <p>Myro, <supplied reason="subaudible">daughter</supplied> of Ptolemaios, aged approximately 13</p></div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <head>Commentary</head>
            <p>Perhaps misread for <foreign xml:lang="grc">γυνή</foreign>, though the subject is rather young.</p>
            <p>Aged about 13; for the formula with <foreign xml:lang="grc">ὡς</foreign>, not otherwise observed in Cyrenaica, cf. SEG
                    VIII. 486-8, 490, 491, 493-5, <!--xref-->from the Jewish cemetery at Tell el Yehudieh in
                    Egypt. It is also common in papyri <!--xref-->.</p>
         </div>
         
